The Queen;;76;;96;;PG-13;;Following the death of Princess Diana in an auto accident, Great Britain's Queen Elizabeth II (Helen Mirren) and Prime Minister Tony Blair (Michael Sheen) struggle to reach a compromise in how the royal family should publicly respond to the tragedy. In the balance is the family's need for privacy and the public's demand for an outward show of mourning.;;Biography,History,Drama;;Stephen Frears;;2006;;Dame Helen Mirren,Michael Sheen,James Cromwell,Helen McCrory,Alex Jennings,Roger Allam,Sylvia Syms,Mark Bazeley,Earl Cameron,Tim McMullan,Paul Barrett,Gavin Park;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_queen